Executive summary
-----------------

This work seeks to harden Apache Cassandra against Byzantine failures.

You can find our client in our forked YCSB project [HardenCassandraYCSB](https://github.com/ronili/HardenCassandraYCSB). 

For more information about Cassandra, see [the Apache Cassandra web site](http://cassandra.apache.org/).

